      "writtenOn": "2018-02-15T05:12:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good point. I wasn\u0027t sure how big to make it, so I just picked \"a bit\" bigger than the 8 bytes of actual data. Is there a better way to estimate/calculate that?",
